org.apache.poi.hwmf.record

Class HwmfDraw.WmfPolyPolygon

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwmf.record.HwmfDraw.WmfPolyPolygon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord, HwmfRecord
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HemfDraw.EmfPolyPolygon
    Enclosing class:
    HwmfDraw 

    public static class HwmfDraw.WmfPolyPolygon
extends java.lang.Object
implements HwmfRecord
    The META_POLYPOLYGON record paints a series of closed polygons. Each polygon is outlined by using the pen and filled by using the brush and polygon fill mode; these are defined in the playback device context. The polygons drawn by this function can overlap.(Meta_POLY POLY GON记录绘制了一系列封闭多边形。每个多边形都是使用笔绘制轮廓的，并使用画笔和多边形填充模式填充;这些都是在播放设备上下文中定义的。该功能绘制的多边形可以重叠。)
